Captain Camil?

116
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:43,410
Yes, it’s me.

117
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,220
Yes!

118
00:09:58,430 --> 00:09:59,290
At that time,

119
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,060
the Saigon Airport

