122
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:12,580
Captain Gu,

123
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,840
it gets me asking you why,

124
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:18,990
are you going the opposite way of your company?

125
00:10:20,650 --> 00:10:22,180
I want to find out the truth.

126
00:10:26,350 --> 00:10:28,990
I certainly appreciate your courage.

127
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:31,610
But I disagree

128
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:34,080
with what you want to do.

129
00:10:39,650 --> 00:10:40,110
Camil.

130
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,530
Camil.

131
00:10:46,570 --> 00:10:47,170
Actually,

132
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:49,730
I'm doing this

133
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:51,790
a faithful girl.

134
00:10:53,230 --> 00:10:55,860
She's a co-pilot at that airline.

135
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:58,600
I've been flying three days straight,

136
00:10:58,660 --> 00:11:00,330
over 40,000 kilometers,

137
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:02,090
just to find a witness,

138
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,080
someone who can testify in court

139
00:11:04,310 --> 00:11:05,440
that she didn't lie.

140
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:14,410
I was exactly like you when I was young.

141
00:11:15,090 --> 00:11:16,260
Crazy for love.

142
00:11:17,830 --> 00:11:19,050
But love is nothing.

143
00:11:20,350 --> 00:11:21,760
And no one will be good.

144
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:24,510
It's not worthy.

145
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:27,520
Camil.

146
00:11:57,180 --> 00:11:58,620
Mr. Liu, I'm sorry.

147
00:12:20,050 --> 00:12:20,700
Mr. Xie

148
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,050
is really

149
00:12:23,710 --> 00:12:25,000
a respectable senior.

150
00:12:33,170 --> 00:12:34,260
The trial is set.

151
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:36,980
It's in three days.

152
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:39,630
Mr. Jiang told me.

153
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:43,010
He asked me to testify in court.

154
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,060
Yicheng.

155
00:12:50,450 --> 00:12:53,380
I know you have your own concerns and consideration.

156
00:12:54,250 --> 00:12:55,370
But only you know

157
00:12:55,570 --> 00:12:56,970
what happened back then.

158
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:00,210
So I still want to ask you

159
00:13:00,850 --> 00:13:02,840
to tell the truth in court.

160
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:24,600
When Doudou grows up,

161
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:28,420
if she know her pilot father

162
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:31,270
can’t even be honest,

163
00:13:33,050 --> 00:13:33,980
what do you think

164
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:36,490
she will think?

165
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:46,920
To be honest,

166
00:13:48,220 --> 00:13:49,480
and true to our duties,

167
00:13:51,090 --> 00:13:52,570
this is the oath we took

168
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:54,050
when we first started.

169
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:00,490
Sorry.

170
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:03,640
Doudou’s waiting for me at home.

171
00:14:03,930 --> 00:14:04,730
I got to leave.

172
00:14:47,410 --> 00:14:48,270
Captain Cheng.

173
00:14:48,710 --> 00:14:49,310
Mr. Liu.

174
00:14:50,110 --> 00:14:51,240
I've made up my mind.

175
00:14:51,310 --> 00:14:53,110
I'm willing to testify in court.

176
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:53,590
Okay.

177
00:14:54,810 --> 00:14:55,280
But

178
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:57,390
I have to remind you.

179
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:58,620
I haven't found

180
00:14:58,650 --> 00:14:59,860
other strong evidence.

181
00:14:59,860 --> 00:15:01,390
The outcome of this case...

182
00:15:01,570 --> 00:15:02,050
I know.

183
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:03,120
It's okay.

184
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:05,690
Send me the time and location.

185
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,130
Okay.

186
00:15:19,350 --> 00:15:20,010
Cheng Xiao,

187
00:15:20,570 --> 00:15:22,880
I need to go on an urgent business trip for a few days.

188
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,140
Take care of yourself.

189
00:15:24,460 --> 00:15:26,620
Trust me. Everything will be fine.

190
00:15:42,340 --> 00:15:51,430
[Two days later]

191
00:15:58,860 --> 00:16:01,190
Cheng Xiao agreed to go to court tomorrow.

192
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:06,190
Okay, got it.

193
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,340
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

194
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,600
See you tomorrow.

195
00:16:19,210 --> 00:16:20,150
It's still off.

196
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:21,800
Song, think about

197
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:23,680
who else we can get in touch with?

198
00:16:25,040 --> 00:16:25,610
It seems

199
00:16:26,160 --> 00:16:27,690
she really made up her mind.

200
00:16:29,830 --> 00:16:30,280
No.

201
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:32,280
She just told me two days ago

202
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:33,710
that she hasn't decided to testify in court yet.

203
00:16:33,710 --> 00:16:34,910
What should we do now?

204
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:37,610
We can't just watch Xiao jump into a fire pit.

205
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:39,280
Xiao told me that she...

206
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:40,750
I know. She told us.

207
00:16:42,280 --> 00:16:43,240
Xiao switched off her phone.

208
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,770
No one can persuade her now.

209
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:45,260
Then...

210
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:47,150
What about Brother Nanting?

211
00:16:47,150 --> 00:16:48,280
He's on sick leave.

212
00:16:48,450 --> 00:16:49,950
He has been out of touch for days.

213
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:51,680
He didn't reply to my messages.

214
00:16:51,950 --> 00:16:53,430
Aren't you his lackey?

215
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:55,720
but you can't even find him at critical moments like this.

216
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:56,250
Oh right,

217
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:58,310
I texted Auntie Qin a few days ago.

218
00:16:58,310 --> 00:16:59,460
She said she had no idea.

219
00:16:59,460 --> 00:17:00,790
But I asked Mr. Ni later.

220
00:17:01,830 --> 00:17:02,630
Brother Zhan?

221
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:05,079
But Mr. Ni said he was busy.

222
00:17:05,099 --> 00:17:06,359
He told me not to worry.

223
00:17:07,390 --> 00:17:08,720
-He’s busy?
-He’s busy?

224
00:17:10,109 --> 00:17:11,880
Didn't you say he's sick?

225
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:14,050
Well...

226
00:17:14,230 --> 00:17:15,510
I have no idea.

227
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:17,810
We can contact either of them.

228
00:17:17,810 --> 00:17:20,339
Why do I feel something big is going to happen?

229
00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:29,410
Xiao,

230
00:17:30,490 --> 00:17:31,820
I can't hear your voice.

231
00:17:32,360 --> 00:17:33,820
What did you use to call me?

232
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:39,280
My phone's out of battery.

233
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:40,940
I called you with my computer.

234
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:43,580
I have to say...

235
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:46,080
You two are really...

236
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:48,470
How did you two end up in court?

237
00:17:48,930 --> 00:17:50,500
This is ridiculous.

238
00:17:52,150 --> 00:17:52,850
How about

239
00:17:53,860 --> 00:17:54,990
I go there tomorrow?

240
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:56,260
No, no, no.

241
00:17:56,860 --> 00:17:58,460
It'll be messier if you come.

242
00:18:00,090 --> 00:18:01,680
Ms. Fang is sure to win.

243
00:18:01,800 --> 00:18:03,060
Don’t worry about her.

244
00:18:03,170 --> 00:18:04,900
What about you?

245
00:18:07,290 --> 00:18:08,560
Don't worry about me.

246
00:18:09,210 --> 00:18:11,140
I'm just telling the truth anyway.

247
00:18:11,250 --> 00:18:12,490
Both of you

248
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:13,820
are so stubborn.

249
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:15,490
Alright.

250
00:18:16,050 --> 00:18:18,090
I'll tell you the result tomorrow.

251
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:19,510
Fine.

252
00:18:20,190 --> 00:18:22,250
Then just tell the truth.

253
00:18:22,700 --> 00:18:24,680
You must control your emotions.

254
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:25,780
Remember,

255
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:27,280
don't be agitated

256
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,040
by the opposing lawyer.

257
00:18:34,990 --> 00:18:35,720
It's so late.

258
00:18:35,950 --> 00:18:37,480
