259
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:39,910
Probably the property management.

260
00:18:39,910 --> 00:18:41,240
Dad, I'll hang up first.

261
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:41,970
Okay.

262
00:18:42,430 --> 00:18:43,690
Take care of yourself.

263
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:45,680
Okay, bye.

264
00:19:03,630 --> 00:19:04,050
You...

265
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:06,400
You...

266
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,130
