267
00:19:11,290 --> 00:19:13,350
I couldn’t persuade the two captains

268
00:19:14,230 --> 00:19:15,770
to testify in court.

269
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:17,560
I'm sorry.

270
00:19:19,440 --> 00:19:20,240
You went to...

271
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:25,920
Thank you.

272
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,140
You've done enough for me.

273
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:35,330
You have to testify in court tomorrow.

274
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:37,920
Don't go. You can't win.

275
00:19:42,710 --> 00:19:43,500
You look

276
00:19:44,280 --> 00:19:45,020
tired.

277
00:19:45,980 --> 00:19:46,980
Go back and rest.

278
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:48,890
Don't testify in court.

279
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:49,890
Let me.

280
00:19:53,520 --> 00:19:54,750
Captain Camil of Mile Airlines

281
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:55,820
told me that

282
00:19:56,390 --> 00:19:58,120
Saigon Airport wasn't closed.

283
00:20:00,350 --> 00:20:00,950
Tomorrow,

284
00:20:01,390 --> 00:20:02,870
I'll testify in court.

285
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:09,170
-But, you will be...
-I’m your Instructor.

