00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:11,100
Anyway, listen to my arrangement.

287
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:15,840
Instructor Gu,

288
00:20:17,290 --> 00:20:18,220
I’ve graduated.

289
00:20:25,490 --> 00:20:26,950
Let's go. I'll see you off.

290
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,660
You can send me to here.

291
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,340
Promise me.

292
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:59,370
Do as I say tomorrow.

293
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:05,250
You have your own ideas.

294
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:06,740
I won't stop you.

295
