00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:21,480
has already begun.

588
00:39:25,760 --> 00:39:26,420
Your Honor.

589
00:39:26,680 --> 00:39:28,480
We request to call a witness to the stand

590
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,260
to testify about

591
00:39:29,260 --> 00:39:31,560
the true situation in the cabin that day.

592
00:39:31,990 --> 00:39:33,720
Witness, please come forward.

593
00:40:09,830 --> 00:40:12,090
I was the observer of the flight that day.

594
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:17,190
After Mr. Guo fell sick,

595
00:40:18,350 --> 00:40:20,660
we applied for diversion first minute

596
00:40:22,340 --> 00:40:24,200
at the earliest possible moment.

597
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:24,950
After that,

598
00:40:25,640 --> 00:40:27,040
Cheng Xiao left the cabin

599
00:40:27,420 --> 00:40:28,880
to check in on the patient.

600
00:40:29,470 --> 00:40:30,150
We received

601
00:40:30,180 --> 00:40:32,310
news from the Saigon Airport Control.

602
00:40:36,510 --> 00:40:37,630
It said...

603
00:40:41,520 --> 00:40:42,110
Yicheng.

604
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:46,360
When Doudou grows up,

605
00:40:48,080 --> 00:40:50,270
if she knew her pilot father

606
00:40:51,240 --> 00:40:53,210
can’t even be honest,

607
00:40:53,780 --> 00:40:54,710
what do you think

608
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:56,860
she will think?

609
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:58,210
Yicheng.

610
00:41:00,980 --> 00:41:03,110
You're an old employee of the company.

611
00:41:03,120 --> 00:41:03,750
I remember

612
00:41:04,350 --> 00:41:05,580
you would attend the company's charity events

613
00:41:05,580 --> 00:41:06,340
every year.

614
00:41:07,730 --> 00:41:08,750
In my impression,

615
00:41:09,240 --> 00:41:10,900
you are not only a good father,

616
00:41:11,080 --> 00:41:12,940
but also a kind and honest person.

617
00:41:27,510 --> 00:41:29,040
According to the notice...

618
00:41:31,430 --> 00:41:32,030
By the way,

619
00:41:32,350 --> 00:41:33,210
one more thing.

620
00:41:33,910 --> 00:41:36,530
Didn’t Dou want to go to that private school?

621
00:41:37,300 --> 00:41:38,430
I've asked someone.

622
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:39,810
It's no problem.

623
00:41:44,430 --> 00:41:46,030
Thank you, Brother-in-law.

624
00:42:02,100 --> 00:42:04,830
We could have made a diversion at Saigon Airport.

625
00:42:27,370 --> 00:42:28,380
At the same time,

626
00:42:29,590 --> 00:42:30,990
the controller also said

627
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:34,460
there were two other planes on standby,

628
00:42:34,460 --> 00:42:36,460
so we had to land as soon as possible.

629
00:42:39,280 --> 00:42:39,880
Witness,

630
00:42:40,320 --> 00:42:42,800
in the air-ground communications played in court just now,

631
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:44,920
The Controller saying that Saigon Airport was closed,

632
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:45,690
Was that in fact

633
00:42:45,690 --> 00:42:47,710
what you heard in the cockpit?

634
00:42:50,530 --> 00:42:50,990
No.
